'''飓风阿尔玛'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Alma}}）是有纪录以来仅有的4个在5月达到飓风强度的[[北大西洋热带气旋|北大西洋热带气旋]]。系统于1970年5月17日在[[巴拿马|巴拿马]]以北发展形成，然后快速增强，于5月20日在[[牙买加|牙买加]]和[[开曼群岛|开曼群岛]]附近达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]130公里的最高强度。风暴在[[古巴|古巴]]以南基本停止移动，并在[[风切变|风切变]]的影响下减弱，到5月22日时已降级成热带低气压。气旋逐渐向西北方向移动，从古巴西部上空经过，再在[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]内重新发展，只是因受风切变限制而无法强化。5月25日，阿尔玛穿越[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]，最终于5月27日在[[弗吉尼亚州|弗吉尼亚州]]近海消散。

风暴首先在牙买加和开曼群岛产生阵风和暴雨，之后减弱期间又在古巴中部和东部引发洪灾，夺走7条人命，另有3000人被迫疏散。佛罗里达州普降中雨，气旋产生的[[雷暴|雷暴天气]]也引起轻度破坏，另有1名女童丧生。风暴湿气之后还继续向美国大西洋海岸扩散，多个沿海州份出现中等程度雨量。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Alma 1970 track.png}}
5月17日晚，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]宣布[[牙买加|牙买加]][[京斯敦|京斯敦]]东南方向约760公里处有热带低气压形成。接下来几天里，气旋向西北方向移动，组织结构渐趋改善，于5月19日进入有利于热带天气系统发展的海域，然后得以快速增强。5月20日，系统成为热带风暴并获名“阿尔玛”（{{lang|en|Alma}}），同时还在[[风切变|风切变]]少、上层[[外流_(气象学)|外流]]强劲和东向内流显著等多重利好因素下继续快速强化。5月20日晚，[[美国海军|美国海军]]侦察机测得系统[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]达到每小时130公里，气象机构之后证实这也是阿尔玛的最高强度。<ref name="tcr1">{{cite report | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1970 | title = Hurricane Alma Preliminary Report (Page 1) | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303193703/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1970-prelim/alma/prelim01.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1970-prelim/alma/prelim01.gif | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-04-27 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | format = [[GIF|GIF]] | date =  }}</ref>截至[[2015年大西洋飓风季|2015年]]，像阿尔玛这样在5月达到飓风标准的[[北大西洋热带气旋|北大西洋热带气旋]]还只有4个<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite report | author = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-021716.txt | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | date = 2016-02-17 | accessdate = 2016-04-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160411090349/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-021716.txt | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-04-11 | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] }}</ref>。

达到最高强度后，飓风的环流和热力格局因西向风切变增多而变得混乱，风暴因此迅速减弱成热带风暴，之后又降级成热带低气压<ref name="tcr1" />。到了5月22日，气旋已在古巴以南洋面基本停止前进，其[[低气压|低气压区]]结构非常混乱，仅有少量降雨和大风，美国国家飓风中心因此停止针对阿尔玛发布公告<ref>{{cite report | author1 = RHS | author2 = GBC | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1970-05-22 | title = Tropical Depression Alma advisory | accessdate = 2016-04-27 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | format = [[JPEG|JPG]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303193906/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0030-jpg/1970/atlantic/alma/marine/tcm2215z.jpg | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0030-jpg/1970/atlantic/alma/marine/tcm2215z.jpg }}</ref>。系统残留继续西进经过开曼群岛，之后又转向北上，从古巴西部上空掠过<ref name="tcr2">{{cite report | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1970 | title = Hurricane Alma Preliminary Report (Page 2) | accessdate = 2016-04-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303210929/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1970-prelim/alma/prelim02.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1970-prelim/alma/prelim02.gif | format = GIF | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | date =  }}</ref>。

5月24日，残留低气压区又开始组织，雷达图像上可以看到渐趋明显的螺旋状[[雨带|雨带]]，气象机构随即将系统重新归类成热带低气压<ref>{{cite report | author = Sugg | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 1970-05-24 | title = Tropical Depression Alma bulletin | accessdate = 2016-04-27 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | format = JPG | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303190347/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0030-jpg/1970/atlantic/alma/public/pub240930z.jpg | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0030-jpg/1970/atlantic/alma/public/pub240930z.jpg }}</ref>。雷达图像还表明，热带低气压的组织结构在逼近佛罗里达州期间依然层次分明，有螺旋状雨带结构将[[风眼|眼状特征]]包裹起来，但在风切变的影响下，风暴的[[对流|对流]]受到限制，强度也无法提高，阿尔玛最终于5月25日以热带低气压强度从佛罗里达州[[锡达礁_(佛罗里达州)|锡达礁]]附近登陆。气旋转向东北穿越[[美国东南部|美国东南部]]，于5月27日在[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]]上空转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。进入[[弗吉尼亚州|弗吉尼亚州]]近海后，风暴残留最终被逐渐逼近的[[冷锋|冷锋]]吸收。<ref name="tcr2" />

== 影响 ==
[[File:Alma_1970_rainfall.png|right]]
阿尔玛于5月21日从[[开曼群岛|开曼群岛]]附近经过，其强度此时已降至低于飓风标准，当地测得的风速达到每小时105公里<ref>{{cite report | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1970 | title = Observations from the Cayman Islands | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0030-jpg/1970/atlantic/alma/sfcdat/s211700z.jpg | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303202503/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0030-jpg/1970/atlantic/alma/sfcdat/s211700z.jpg | accessdate = 2016-04-27 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | format = JPG | date =  }}</ref>。牙买加也降下暴雨，风力达到烈风强度<ref>{{cite report | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1970 | title = Hurricane Alma Marie Advisory | accessdate = 2016-04-27 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | format = JPG | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303192829/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0030-jpg/1970/atlantic/alma/marine/tcm2116z.jpg | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0030-jpg/1970/atlantic/alma/marine/tcm2116z.jpg | date =  }}</ref>。古巴中部和东部在风暴经过前就降下暴雨，引起山洪爆发<ref name="tcr2" />，造成7人遇难，多户民宅被毁。面对洪灾威胁，[[东方省|东方省]]有约3000人撤离。该国另有16家糖厂因天气恶劣停工，进度已经落后的糖类作物收割又要进一步延迟。<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = The Miami News | year = 1970 | title = Seven Cubans Drown in Floods of Alma}}</ref>

阿尔玛的残留令佛罗里达州普降大雨，局部地区降雨量达到127毫米以上。[[迈阿密|迈阿密]]附近地区雨量最高，达169毫米<ref name="rainfall">{{cite report | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1970 | title = Hurricane Alma — Rainfall | accessdate = 2016-04-27 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/alma1970filledrainblk.gif | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304064432/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/alma1970filledrainblk.gif | deadurl = no | format = GIF | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | date =  }}</ref>。这些降水虽然有助于缓解当地旱情<ref name="tcr2" />，但雷暴天气又导致[[佛罗里达礁岛群|佛罗里达礁岛群]]及州内其它多地的车辆驾驶变得更危险<ref>{{cite report | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1970 | title = Thunderstorms in the Florida Keys | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0030-jpg/1970/atlantic/alma/local/eyw250043.jpg | accessdate = 2016-04-27 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | format = JPG | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303234245/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0030-jpg/1970/atlantic/alma/local/eyw250043.jpg | date =  }}</ref>。佛罗里达州海岸沿线发布小型船只警告<ref>{{cite report | author = [[美国国家气象局|National Weather Service]] | year = 1970 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303182658/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0030-jpg/1970/atlantic/alma/local/fmy241000edt.jpg | title = Fort Myers Weather Statement | accessdate = 2016-04-27 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0030-jpg/1970/atlantic/alma/local/fmy241000edt.jpg | deadurl = no | format = JPG | date =  }}</ref>。迈阿密有一名女童因[[闪电|闪电]]遇难<ref>{{cite report | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1970 | title = Deaths from Hurricane Alma | accessdate = 2016-04-27 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303193957/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0030-jpg/1970/atlantic/alma/postevent/deaths.jpg | format = JPG | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0030-jpg/1970/atlantic/alma/postevent/deaths.jpg | date =  }}</ref>，[[麦尔兹堡|麦尔兹堡]]有部分附属建筑和屋顶因雷暴天气受损<ref>{{cite report | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1970 | title = Wind Damage Reports from Alma | accessdate = 2016-04-27 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303194945/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0030-jpg/1970/atlantic/alma/postevent/wind_241543z.jpg | format = JPG | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0030-jpg/1970/atlantic/alma/postevent/wind_241543z.jpg | date =  }}</ref>。[[圣彼德斯堡_(佛罗里达州)|圣彼德斯堡]]约400户家庭的电话服务因洪灾中断<ref name="saintpetersburgtimes" />。[[梅米特岛_(佛罗里达州)|梅米特岛]]（{{lang|en|Merritt Island}}）测得时速72公里的阵风<ref>{{cite report | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 1970 | title = Merritt Island Wind Reports | accessdate = 2016-04-27 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303194945/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0030-jpg/1970/atlantic/alma/postevent/maxwind.jpg | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | format = JPG | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/cdmp/dvd0030-jpg/1970/atlantic/alma/postevent/maxwind.jpg | date =  }}</ref>。此外，阿尔玛在[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]]、[[南卡罗莱纳州|南卡罗莱纳州]]、北卡罗莱纳州、弗吉尼亚州和[[马里兰州|马里兰州]]产生中等程度雨量，局部地区达到76毫米<ref name="rainfall" />。风暴残留还在南卡罗莱纳州[[哥伦比亚_(南卡罗莱纳州)|哥伦比亚]]附近催生出一场[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]，致使一套房屋的屋顶被毁<ref name="saintpetersburgtimes">{{cite news | newspaper = Saint Petersburg Times | year = 1970 | title = Alma Brings an End to the Drought | accessdate = 2016-04-27 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=R_0NAAAAIBAJ&sjid=AXwDAAAAIBAJ&pg=5473,4156534&dq=alma&hl=en | archive-date = 2020-12-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201221135944/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=R_0NAAAAIBAJ&sjid=AXwDAAAAIBAJ&pg=5473%2C4156534&dq=alma&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

